                )

            [content] => <span style="font-weight:400;">If Christmas day is meant for comfy pants and stuffing yourself silly with all the festive deliciousness you can stand, then New Year’s Eve should be synonymous with the clinking of champagne glasses, the people who’ve made your year special, and a sense of excitement at all the promise of a fresh year full of potential. If you’re not settled on your NYE plans yet, here are a few ideas to consider!</span>
<h3><strong>1. <b>Pyjama Party</b></strong></h3>
<span style="font-weight:400;">Sometimes, the best nights out are the ones spent all cosy at home with onesies, fluffy slippers, and yummy food and drinks to warm the soul. Invite your nearest and dearest, sort out a Spotify playlist, and ring in the New Year in comfort. Can’t host your event at home? Don’t worry - there are loads of <a href="http://www.shortletsmalta.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">great properties in Malta</a> that you can rent out for the event! </span>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/media/PKAR7jz7tr8qY/giphy.webp" />
<h3><strong>2. <b>Rock out with Red Electrick</b></strong></h3>
https://www.facebook.com/events/1520902357999172/

<span style="font-weight:400;">Get your tickets sorted and get ready for what promises to be a fabulous night out at Hugo’s Terrace! Home-grown talent, Red Electrick, are set to give you a truly spectacular performance, and you’ll love getting dressed up, snapping loads of photos, and sipping on those sinfully good cocktails. </span>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/media/26u44jd37WP8Coa1W/giphy.webp" />
<h3><strong>3. <b>#Throwback at Tattingers </b></strong></h3>
http://https//www.facebook.com/events/849017055268100/

<span style="font-weight:400;">Party and raise your glasses to the sound of the 80s and 90s, expertly mixed by Djs Clint Bajada, Alfred Zammit, Noel Camilleri, and Chris Funkytown. As you dance your way to midnight and beyond at Tattingers, perched just on the side of the historic Rabat, you’ll be filled with nostalgia for the parties of the past, and buzzing with excitement for the year to come all at once. Cheers!</span>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/media/l2Je8gqSxgoW6ebSg/giphy.webp" />
<h3><strong>4. <b>A Royal NYE in Valletta</b></strong></h3>
https://www.facebook.com/events/543832645956733/

<span style="font-weight:400;">Hit Kingsway in our gorgeous capital city for a fancy night out featuring jazz and electro-swing music, divine canapés, and all the sumptuous cocktails and drinks you’ll need to celebrate the New Year. </span>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/media/26ybweGW1bMIoHoyY/giphy.webp" />
<h3><strong>5. <b>Luxury at TwentyTwo</b></strong></h3>
https://www.facebook.com/events/168576373739686/

<span style="font-weight:400;">EBM presents Dom Perignon New Year’s Eve Party at TwentyTwo - the prefect night out if you’re looking for stunning sophistication, fireworks, and expertly-mixed drinks at one of the most exclusive venues on the island. </span>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/media/l2R03Nb2iQj9oyqv6/giphy.webp" />
<h3><strong>6. </strong><b>Winter Wine Night</b></h3>
<span style="font-weight:400;">If you’d rather do something a little more low key with your significant other or maybe just a few loved ones, then book yourself a table at one of the island’s favourite wine bars for a night filled with good conversation, fine wine, and your other great loves: cheeseboards and close friends. If you’re not sure where to go, here are a few of our personal favourites when it comes to wine nights:</span>
<ul>
	<li style="font-weight:400;"><span style="font-weight:400;">Del Borgo, Birgu</span></li>
	<li style="font-weight:400;"><span style="font-weight:400;">Legligin, Valletta</span></li>
	<li style="font-weight:400;"><span style="font-weight:400;">StrEat, Valletta</span></li>
	<li style="font-weight:400;"><span style="font-weight:400;">Sensations, Birkirkara</span></li>
	<li style="font-weight:400;"><span style="font-weight:400;">Fra Giuseppe, Balzan</span></li>
	<li style="font-weight:400;"><span style="font-weight:400;">Trabuxu, Valletta</span></li>
	<li style="font-weight:400;"><span style="font-weight:400;">Rocksalt, St. Julian’s </span></li>
	<li style="font-weight:400;"><span style="font-weight:400;">Cellini, Naxxar </span></li>
	<li style="font-weight:400;"><span style="font-weight:400;">Sistina Wine amp; Co, Sliema</span></li>
</ul>
<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/media/u97BO3m556gGk/giphy.webp" />
<b><i>What are you doing this NYE? Tell us in a comment! </i></b>
