            [title] => SimpleXMLElement Object
                (
                    [0] => Which property best fits your holiday personality?
                )

            [date] => SimpleXMLElement Object
                (
                    [0] => 2018-03-14 10:46:21
                )

            [content] => "western" >Choosing a holiday home is very much like choosing your own home – this will be the place you will spend time in when you’re not out exploring when you need to rest your head after a day touring around the island. Some might choose this abode haphazardly, not giving it much thought. Yet there are different properties for different personalities, and at Short Lets Malta (<a href="http://www.shortletsmalta.com">www.shortletsmalta.com</a>) you’re spoilt for choice when browsing for your ideal holiday home. Take a look below at our five different holiday personalities, and the vacation properties which match their traits!
"western"><b>If you're a relaxation enthusiast - </b><b><a href="http://shortletsmalta.com/Carob-Hills_Villa_Blu.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Villa Blu</a></b>

<h1><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4209" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/simon_mellieha_night_026.jpg" alt="simon_mellieha_night_026" width="5720" height="3813" /></h1>
"western" >With its secluded location and blue hues, this Villa is sure to drain the stress out of your life and engulf you in calmness. Sweat out your worries in the sizzling sauna, then take a dip in the refreshing infinity pool, or bask in the summer sun on the pool deck and leave all your troubles behind. You can even hire a private chef so that you won't even have to worry about what's for dinner! The peaceful decor of this villa is reminiscent of the beach - turquoise hues meet neutral tones, with faint hints of the seaside cropping up even on the living room cushions. This villa will reset your mind and give you the much-needed break that you crave.
 

[gallery ids="4251,4248" type="rectangular" link="none"]
"western" ><b>If you're after a fun-filled vacation - <a href="http://shortletsmalta.com/Carob-Hills_Villa_Goa.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Villa Goa</a></b>
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4210" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/ralph_mellieha_day_014.jpg" alt="ralph_mellieha_day_014.jpg" width="6016" height="4016" />
"western" >Villa Goa is a fun-lover's paradise - with a huge variety of in-house activities to choose from: you can take a dip in the infinity pool, play pool in the downstairs games room, challenge your friends to a game of Xbox, or table soccer... The list of fun-packed activities found in this huge home is endless. If you ever get tired of enjoying what the house has to offer, you can always choose one of the many activities on <a href="http://www.funmalta.com/">www.funmalta.com</a> - your online amusement park - where you can choose between paragliding or horse-riding, quad-biking or yachting, and much, much more! If you're after a memorable, action-filled holiday with family or friends, this Villa is definitely the choice for you.
<b></b>
 

[gallery ids="4249,4250" type="rectangular" link="none"]
"western"><b>If you like the finer things in life - </b><b></b><b><a href="http://shortletsmalta.com/040-Amazing-Valletta-Harbour-Views-2-bd.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazing Valletta Harbour Views 2-bd</a></b>
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4211" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/balcony.jpg" alt="balcony.jpg" width="1229" height="820" />
"western" >If, like fine wines, you prefer the more sophisticated side of life, then this stunning apartment is the ideal abode for your Malta travels. Located in the European Capital of Culture 2018, in the gorgeous Valletta - which in itself is an open-air museum - this beautiful apartment is modernly decorated and consists of all the amenities you might need on your Malta holiday. With a magnificent sea view balconies overlooking the historic Grand Harbour, and situated above Valletta's old entrance - Victoria Gate - you'll feel right at home sipping fine Maltese wine and enjoying this eternal city. The apartment retains its Maltese charm through the traditional wooden balconies which flood the holiday home in natural light. You'll be at the heart of all cultural events, a perfect place to be for a truly enchanting holiday.
 

[gallery ids="4254,4255" type="rectangular" link="none"]
"western" ><b>If you're a business traveller - <a href="http://shortletsmalta.com/Astounding_Views__4-bedroom_Apt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tigne 44</a></b>
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4212" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/tigne44.jpg" alt="tigne44" width="1000" height="547" />
"western" >If you're in Malta on business, chances are you'd rather reside in the business district of the island - Sliema or St Julian’s. This 4-bedroom apartment in Sliema is at the heart of its business centre, while also enjoying a breath-taking view over the harbour towards Valletta. While life in Sliema resembles city life with its bustling businesses, its rush hour traffic and its many residents rushing to and fro, by night this town is transformed into an entertainment hub, with a myriad of bars opening their doors for after-work drinks, going on until the wee hours of the morning. This apartment is just the ticket - being close enough to Sliema centre that you can walk to any meeting, while also being far enough from the bars so that you can enjoy a good night's sleep. You truly get the best of both worlds, and while you're here on business, it would be a shame to just enjoy the business side of the town!
 

[gallery ids="4256,4257" type="rectangular" link="none"]
"western" ><b>If you're on a budget - <a href="http://shortletsmalta.com/Remarkable_1-bedroom_Apartment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Muriel Apartment</a></b>
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4259 aligncenter" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/portrait-362-db34f7332727cac6355f16ce56e53a5dd20952a64d2ef05af63c031fc0e56207.jpg" alt="PORTRAIT-362-db34f7332727cac6355f16ce56e53a5dd20952a64d2ef05af63c031fc0e56207" width="546" height="362" />
"western" >If money is tight and you're looking for a low-cost holiday in sunny Malta, then Muriel one-bedroom apartment is just right for you. With budget-friendly prices, this apartment places you right in the action without forking out the dough. Fully equipped for home-cooking (meaning you'll save on restaurants) and decorated in a modern style, you'll feel like you're getting more for your buck, as the location alone is worth its price. Just 7 minutes away from the bus stop to Valletta, this apartment is the perfect base for exploring the island, all while not breaking the bank!
 

[gallery ids="4260,4261" type="rectangular"]
"western" ><i>Did we forget to mention your personality type? Worry not! Head over to <a href="http://www.shortletsmalta.com">www.shortletsmalta.com</a> and find out the right holiday home for you!</i>

<img height="1" width="1" style="display:none;" alt="" src="https://dc.ads.linkedin.com/collect/?pid=257873amp;conversionId=333177amp;fmt=gif" />
