            [title] => SimpleXMLElement Object
                (
                    [0] => What’s on in August
                )

            [date] => SimpleXMLElement Object
                (
                    [0] => 2018-08-01 11:01:00
                )

            [content] => <a name="_GoBack"></a><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">August in Malta is one of the busiest and bustling months of the year – festas abound, outdoor events take place every weekend – there is always something to do in Malta during this sweltering summer month. The most prominent of all festas is undoubtedly the festa of the Assumption of Our Lady, or as it is most known among the Maltese, Santa Marija. The 15</span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">th</span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"> of August is in fact a public holiday here in Malta, and the feast is celebrated in 9 different towns across Malta and Gozo. Want to know where to head this August? Keep on reading!</span>
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>15</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> August Santa Marija</b></span>
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">The festa of Santa Marija is celebrated in Mqabba, Qrendi, Mosta, Gudja, Attard, Ghaxaq, Birkirkara, Zebbug and Victoria, Gozo. The Maltese have an ancient tradition called the ‘Seba’ Santa Marijiet’, where a pilgrimage of the 7 most prominent Santa Marija festa celebrations was done on the feast day. Nowadays, you can create your very own ‘Seba’ Santa Marijiet’ by visiting these festas:</span>
<img class=" size-full wp-image-4687 aligncenter" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/santa-marija-festa-mosta-the-assumption-of-our-lady.jpg" alt="santa-marija-festa-mosta-the-assumption-of-our-lady.jpg" width="640" height="480" />
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b><a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/feast-of-the-assumption-of-our-lady-11620?map=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Santa Marija, Mosta</a> </b></span>
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b><a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/feast-of-the-assumption-of-our-lady-11619?map=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Santa Marija, Qrendi</a>
</b></span>
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b><a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/feast-of-the-assumption-of-our-lady-11621?map=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Santa Marija, Gudja</a></b></span><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><a name="_GoBack"></a></span>
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b><a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/feast-of-the-assumption-of-our-lady-11618?map=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Santa Marija, Attard</a>
</b></span>
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b><a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/feast-of-the-assumption-of-our-lady-11634?map=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Santa Marija, Ghaxaq</a></b></span>
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b><a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/feast-of-the-assumption-of-our-lady-11616?map=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Santa Marija, Mqabba</a></b></span>
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b><a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/feast-of-the-assumption-of-our-lady-11617" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Santa Marija, Victoria, Gozo</a>
</b></span>
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>Other Events</b></span>
<a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/robin-schulz-at-caf-del-mar-11935" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>Robin Schultz at Cafe Del Mar – 5</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> August, Café del Mar, Qawra</b></span></a>
<img class=" size-full wp-image-4682 aligncenter" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/robin-schultz.jpg" alt="Oliver_Heldens_FB_Covers" width="365" height="245" />
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">World-renowned DJ Robin Schiltz will be manning the decks this 5th August at popular seaside venue Cafe del Mar, ensuring solid tunes and groovy beats throughout the night. Clubbers and ravers can enjoy the German DJ’s set until the early hours of the morning, the ideal recipe for a truly memorable Maltese night! </span>
<a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/delicata-wine-festival-11814" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>Delicata Wine Festival – from the 9</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> to the 12</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> August, Upper Barrakka Gardens, Valletta</b></span></a>
<img class=" size-full wp-image-4680 aligncenter" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/delicata.png" alt="delicata" width="299" height="168" />
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">Our annual date with decadent wine is back, with a whole weekend dedicated to fine Maltese wine, great atmosphere, sweeping views and live entertainment. Capture the true sense of the Maltese laid-back attitude, wine glass in hand, looking over to the exquisitely-lit Three Cities – and bask in the Mediterranean-ness of it all. </span>
<a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/ministry-of-sound-tours-malta-presents-darude-11971" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>Ministry of Sound Tours Malta present Darude – 11</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> August, Club Phoenix, Gianpula Village</b></span></a>
<img class=" size-full wp-image-4679 aligncenter" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/darude.png" alt="darude" width="365" height="279" />
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">Another event for dance music lovers! Established DJ Darude will be hitting the island’s shores on the 11</span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">th</span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"> of August, delivering good tunes and a fantastic vibe at Club Phoenix in Gianpula Village. Accompanied by some of the most well-loved DJs in the local scene, this Finnish DJ is sure to bring the house down. </span>
<a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/summer-daze-11845" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>Summer Daze Malta – 14</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> and 15</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> August, Ta’ Qali National Park amp; Café del Mar</b></span></a>
<img class=" size-full wp-image-4678 aligncenter" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/summer-daze.jpg" alt="summer daze" width="365" height="228" />
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">August brings us a ton of open-air events, and Summer Daze Malta is a prime example! Set over two days in two outdoor venues, the festival will bring international artists and DJs together for a truly unforgettable two day music-fest. Day One sees international superstar Rita Ora perform live at Ta’ Qali National Park, while Day Two presents Grammy-award winning DJ Roger Sanchez to the decks at Café del Mar – ensuring a massive event that you cannot miss!</span>
<a href="https://www.visitmalta.com/en/event-details/2018-08/glitch-festival-11291" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>Glitch Festival – 14</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> to the 16</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> August, Gianpula Fields</b></span></a>
<img class=" size-full wp-image-4677 aligncenter" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/glitch.jpg" alt="glitch" width="365" height="245" />
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">After a highly successful two-years, Glitch Festival is back with a bang! Having moved from September to the more-accessible August dates, this year’s festival is headlined by a whole crew of world-renowned techno, electro and house DJs: Nina Kraviz, Jeff Mills, Amelie Lens, Rodhad, Dax J and Dopplereffekt to name but a few. The festival is spread over a two-day rave at Gianpula Fields, as well as a boat-party on the 16</span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">th</span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"> August – to end the Festival in truly Maltese fashion. This is not an event to be missed!</span>
<a href="https://www.whatson.com.mt/en/events/events/15864/fireworks-spectacular-2018.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>Fireworks Spectacular 2018 – 14</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> August, Mqabba</b></span></a>
<img class=" size-full wp-image-4676 aligncenter" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/fireworks.jpg" alt="fireworks" width="445" height="320" />
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">August is not just about clubbing, it’s about bombastic firework shows too! Mqabba is one of the best-known localities for its spectacular and intricate fireworks, and the pyrotechnic company have won many prestigious awards for their firework displays. Festa season is always the best time to witness some truly artistic and colourful displays of fireworks, with a one and a half hour pyrotechnic show which will include 10,000 shots synchronised to music. If you’re in Malta during this season, this is the fireworks show to watch!</span>
<a href="https://www.whatson.com.mt/en/events/events/15654/edvin-marton-stradivarius-concert-show.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>Edvin Morton: Stradivarius Concert Show – 25</b></span><sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b>th</b></span></sup><span style="font-family:Arial, serif;"><b> August, Pjazza Teatru Rjal, Valletta</b></span></a>
<img class=" size-full wp-image-4681 aligncenter" src="https://shortletsmalta.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/edvin-marton.png" alt="edvin marton" width="445" height="320" />
<span style="font-family:Arial, serif;">If a more classical type of music is what you’re after, then you certainly cannot miss Emmy-award winning Edvin Morton’s Stradivarius Concert show. The violin mastermind is back to enthral the crowds at Valletta after the huge success of the Rock Symphony of 2017. </span>

