<b>1 | Wonder Woman Midnight Premiere (1</b><sup><b>st</b></sup><b> June)</b>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/l0HlymZ7Jv6JoiYjC.webp" />

It’s finally Wonder Woman’s time to shine – and talented actress and model, Gal Gadot, is just the woman for the job. Even if you’re not a proud comic book geek, you’ll still enjoy watching this long-anticipated superhero spectacular.

<a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/656024887938706/">https://www.facebook.com/events/656024887938706/</a>



<b>2 | The Grid 2017 (3</b><sup><b>rd</b></sup><b> June)</b>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/eS1lKEnFu37eo.webp" />



We talked about<a href="http://blog.shortletsmalta.com/2017/05/05/the-grid-2017-maltas-toughest-obstacle-race/"> The Grid, ‘Malta’s toughest obstacle race’</a><!-- https://blog.shortletsmalta.com/2017/05/05/the-grid-2017-maltas-toughest-obstacle-race/ -->, in one of our blogs earlier this month. If you think you have what it takes to take on this fitness challenge, then head over to Pemroke this June to see what you can <i>really</i> do. You’ve got this.

<a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/1053800501323845/">https://www.facebook.com/events/1053800501323845/</a>

<b>3 | BLANK Earth Garden (4</b><sup><b>th</b></sup><b> June)</b>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/l0MYJnJQ4EiYLxvQ4.webp" />



BLANK has quickly become synonymous with incredible parties with the perfect summer vibe, so why not kick things off with BLANK Earth Garden and spend the day dancing your heart out in Ta Qali?

Event page: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/736119739899889/">https://www.facebook.com/events/736119739899889/</a>

<b>4 | A Thing Called Hip Hop Vol.2 (9</b><sup><b>th</b></sup><b> June)</b>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/wAxlCmeX1ri1y.webp" />

Funky Monkey is a cool little venue on Manoel Island and the perfect place to hit if you want to go beyond the usual entertainment hotspots. For a weekend that is truly off the hook, be sure to check out A Thing Called Hip Hop!

Event page: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/461957400814870/">https://www.facebook.com/events/461957400814870/</a>



<b>5 | From a Distance: Gulja Holland (Until 24</b><sup><b>th</b></sup><b> June)<!-- Photo attached  --></b>

Talented local artist Gulja Holland will be presenting brand new collection of vibrant abstract paintings entitled ‘From a Distance’. The series of thought-provoking paintings is inspired by some of the most pressing environmental issues of our time. Art lovers, take note!

Event page: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/776138775887948/">https://www.facebook.com/events/776138775887948/</a>

<b>6 | Afternoon Tea at Le Café (Until 16</b><sup><b>th</b></sup><b> June)</b>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/CKcgUDxMvIIx2.webp" />



Grab a couple of your besties and head down to The Corinthia Hotel in St. George’s Bay for a spot of afternoon tea and some sinfully good cakes! You definitely won’t regret this little bit of indulgence.

Event page: <a href="http://www.corinthia.com/en/hotels/malta-stgeorgesbay/dining/bars/le-cafe/afternoon-tea">http://www.corinthia.com/en/hotels/malta-stgeorgesbay/dining/bars/le-cafe/afternoon-tea</a>

<strong><b>7 | Pub Crawl Summer Launch (16</b><sup><b>th</b></sup><b> June)</b></strong>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/1vh1PXneQqN1e.webp" />



Go hard or go home! This pub crawl takes you to five different bars to give you the ultimate start to your Maltese summer. If you love to party, then you definitely won’t want to miss this.

<a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/1469023089827820/">https://www.facebook.com/events/1469023089827820/</a>

<b>8 | No Class (23</b><sup><b>rd</b></sup><b> June)</b>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/3EfgWHj0YIDrW.webp" />



Get a cheeky taste of all the things that make us ‘typically Maltese’ while enjoying what promises to be a fantastic playlist to get you moving.

<a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/114745972423544/">https://www.facebook.com/events/114745972423544/</a>

<b>9 | British Choral Classics (24</b><sup><b>th</b></sup><b> June)</b>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/PRQ6McRJQ4vnO.webp" />



If you’re in the mood for something a little more classical, then this might be right up your alley. The Ealing Choral Society will be performing at St. Paul’s Pro-Cathedral in our stunning capital city, Valletta.

<a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/1831548473773041/">https://www.facebook.com/events/1831548473773041/</a>

<b>10 | Isle of MTV Malta Music Week (23</b><sup><b>rd</b></sup><b> – 28</b><sup><b>th</b></sup><b> June)</b>

<img class=" aligncenter" src="https://i.giphy.com/Qw4X3FyDEfQrNgjl6M0.webp" />

The much-anticipated Isle of MTV Malta Music week is finally here! For a full week of incredible events just buzzing with summer excitement, check out all the events on offer in the run up to the all-important concert on the 27<sup>th</sup> June, where The Chainsmokers will be headlining this year.

<a href="https://www.facebook.com/pg/IsleofMTVMalta/events/">https://www.facebook.com/pg/IsleofMTVMalta/events/</a>


