            [blog_content] => Have you ever wondered what lies beneath your feet? A network of secret passages lies beneath our beautiful capital. Discover another world when visiting Valletta, Europe's capital of culture 2018. The cisterns are open to the public for the first time until <span class="aBn"><span class="aQJ">1st July as a part of major <a href="https://valletta2018.org/news/valletta-2018-opens-underground-cisterns-as-part-of-major-exhibition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">exhibition</a> Dal-Baħar Madwarha (The Island is What the Sea Surrounds).</span></span>

