https://www.instagram.com/p/BhyY2nfnTfd/?taken-by=landofwildhearts

<strong>1. Sunrise on a rocky Sliema beach</strong>

https://www.instagram.com/p/Bh3uv3-gsMF/?tagged=malta

<i><b>Want to see all the very best that our island has to offer? Check out all the </b></i><a href="https://www.funmalta.com/"><span style="color:#1155cc;"><i><u><b>best activities in Malta</b></u></i></span></a><i><b> over at FunMalta! </b></i>
