	<li>Very good knowledge of Maltese, English and another foreign language.</li>
	<li>Possess excellent verbal and written communication skills.</li>
	<li>Have a positive outlook and be pro-active to handle client requests.</li>
	<li>Organised, takes initiative and smart in appearance.</li>
	<li>Possess a valid Maltese driving licence and a clean police conduct.</li>
	<li>Experience in customer relations/hospitality/front desk duties will be considered an asset.</li>
</ul>
<b>Office Administrator</b>
The role requires a highly-motivated person with proven experience in office administration, excellent skills in coordinating works between all Departments and to assist the Management Team.
