	<li>Handle all calls during office hours</li>
	<li>Work closely with the Management Team</li>
	<li>Follow up enquiries and coordinate works between departments</li>
	<li>Reply to clients' queries and handle any issues and/or complaints</li>
	<li>Support the Company’s daily operations</li>
